      <title>黛比威胁南卡罗来纳州沿海地区和其他地区，带来历史性洪水</title>
      <link>https://www.npr.org/2024/08/06/nx-s1-5064342/debby-threatens-coastal-south-carolina-and-other-regions-with-historic-flooding</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在南卡罗来纳州，飓风黛比的残余正在横扫该州，人们被敦促不要上路。这场风暴沿着海岸缓缓移动，席卷了佛罗里达州和乔治亚州。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.npr.org/2024/08/06/nx-s1-5064342/debby-threatens-coastal-south-carolina-and-other-regions-with-historic-flooding</guid>
